      <title>想象的到的情况更容易被高估发生的可能性</title>
      <link>https://tongluoshao.space/permanent/%E6%83%B3%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%A2%AB%E9%AB%98%E4%BC%B0%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7/</link>
